commit_list.message:
Fix gradient animation, add sine waves

Gradient was skipping on a ring because the length was off by one. Also
made the vertical edge of the ramp into a reverse ramp to avoid stepping
effect on each pixel at low frequencies.  Added a standing wave
animation intended for rings.

commit_list.message:
Switch from WebSockets to OPC client

Hitting message truncation bug with the websockets client when
addressing fadecandy channel 5 and up. Switched to poorly translated OPC
client to circumvent the problem.

Also made LED region aware of multiple strips.
